<<indent 6 "here’s the pencil, make it work">>
<<linkreplace "''.''">>.
    <<append "#bedwindow" t8n>>If the window is on your right, you are in your own bed.<</append>>
<</linkreplace>>
<<linkreplace "''.''">>.
    <<append "#heartwindow" t8n>>If the window<br>
<<indent 3 "is over your heart, and it is painted shut, then we are breathing">><br>
river water.<</append>>
<</linkreplace>>
<<linkreplace "''.''">>.
